md:note.div:
Digtsamling af Šihāb al-Dīn Ahmad ibn al-Husayn Ibn al-'Ulayf al-Makkī (d. 926 H [1520].
Erhvervet i Kairo 1763 (d. 1763) af den danske filolog Frederik Christian von Haven, der var deltager i Carsten Niebuhrs ekspedition til Mellemøsten 1761-1767.
Cod.Arab. 244

Poetry collection by Šihāb al-Dīn Ahmad ibn al-Husayn Ibn al-'Ulayf al-Makkī (d. 926 H [1520 CE].
Bought in Cairo 1763 (d. 1763) by the Danish philogist Frederik Christian von Haven, a member of the Carsten Niebuhr ekspedition 1761-1767.
